description: Relaunch, price reduction and ready to move!!!Welcome to your new home on the Eastside! Fantastic opportunity for first time buyer or investor.  Featuring 2+ bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, this home offers comfortable living within its 1100 square feet. Many new updates include all new stainless steel appliances (Factory blue seal on for protection until closing), new kitchen flooring, hardwood floors refinished, new carpeting in bedrooms and the entire unit has been freshly painted!!   There is an additional room on the main level that can be used as a den/office or 3rd bedroom.  Additionally there is room on the lower level for a small office.  There is an outdoor space for grilling and an upgraded heat/hot water tankless system.  Perfectly positioned, this home awaits your personal touch. Don’t miss out!!
